# Logs Directory

This directory stores M-Pesa transaction logs.

Logs are automatically created when you make API calls:
- mpesa_YYYY-MM-DD.log - API requests and responses
- stk_callbacks_YYYY-MM-DD.log - STK Push callbacks
- c2b_validation_YYYY-MM-DD.log - C2B validation callbacks
- c2b_confirmation_YYYY-MM-DD.log - C2B confirmation callbacks
- b2c_results_YYYY-MM-DD.log - B2C result callbacks

Note: Log files are automatically ignored by git (.gitignore)
